      <h3>Speed</h3>
  <p>ExpressVPN consistently delivers excellent speeds with its Lightway protocol. NordVPN is also very fast with NordLynx. Both are excellent with slight edge to ExpressVPN. In head-to-head testing, we found that both tools deliver competent results but differ significantly in their approach. ExpressVPN focuses on providing a streamlined, beginner-friendly experience while NordVPN offers more depth and customization for advanced users. The choice between them often comes down to whether you prioritize ease of use or granular control.</p>
    <h3>Security</h3>
  <p>Both have audited no-logs policies. ExpressVPN TrustedServer technology ensures no data on hard drives. NordVPN Double VPN adds extra encryption layers. Our testing revealed that both platforms have distinct advantages depending on the specific task. ExpressVPN excels in scenarios requiring quick results and intuitive workflows. NordVPN shines when dealing with complex requirements that benefit from its advanced feature set. Understanding your specific needs will help determine which tool is better suited for your work.</p>
