    <p>Both ExpressVPN and NordVPN offer tiered pricing models designed to accommodate different user segments. ExpressVPN provides a generous free tier that includes core features suitable for individuals and small projects. Upgrading to a paid plan unlocks advanced functionality, higher usage limits, and priority support. NordVPN offers competitive pricing with its own free tier and premium plans that add feature depth and capacity. The value proposition differs based on which features matter most to you. For budget-conscious users, both platforms offer affordable entry points. At the professional level, pricing is comparable with variations based on included features and user limits. Enterprise plans are available for both platforms, offering custom pricing, dedicated support, and advanced security features. We recommend taking advantage of free trials to evaluate which platform delivers better value for your specific use case before committing to a paid subscription.</p>

